40:03.334 --> 40:04.334
Happy birthday.
Happy birthday!

40:04.336 --> 40:07.337
The last time you two
celebrated a birthday together

40:07.339 --> 40:09.005
you were three years old.

40:09.007 --> 40:09.739
I want you to stay.

40:09.741 --> 40:10.874
I know you have to do
what you have to do.

40:10.876 --> 40:14.244
I can't stay here and be with
my mom at the same time, okay?

40:14.246 --> 40:17.914
I have to choose.
You should not go.

40:17.916 --> 40:20.383
Are you cheating
on David?

40:20.385 --> 40:22.752
I don't know what I want.
